      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STRAIGHT OUT (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Last start finished 3rd over 324m at this track beaten 3.5 lengths (18.03) behind FUMBLES in a Mix 3/4 on June 4. With a clean break looks hard to beat. FUMBLES (4) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 7 (17.80). Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. FANTASTIC IRIS (6) was fresh up last time at Wentworth Park where she finished fourth (30.19) in a Mix 2/3. Will strip fitter for the run. The form out of her last race has been franked. Shapes as one to consider. PINCH POINT (2) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
